window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Millions on Earth are shaken by the events set in motion by Zack's final play. Billions on Tygon watch breathlessly as the consequences of his actions ripple through both worlds. Will his girlfriend, still inside the Game, step forward to lead the movement that he created? </p> <p>Billions of lives are in jeopardy of being lost based on the decisions made by children inside the Game. </p>"; 
